data.text:
Ever thought, “Hey, I’ve heard that song before” but couldn’t remember where? It’s quite possible the big hit you swear you’ve heard before was cut on another artist’s album but was never released as a single. We’ve put together a database of such songs in the hopes that it’ll inspire you to dig out some of your old CD’s and discover some new old music! If you know of any other songs that fit this criteria, please email us at info@hometowncountrymusic.com to let us know so we can add them…thanks!
